# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Dardanup

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 60 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Dardanup, of which four are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following four state registered places within the Shire of Dardanup:
